Bearings are often generic. It may be possible to obtain a bearing from a
manufacturer/distributor if you can supply the specs. Here are a couple of
links to get you started:

http://tinyurl.com/yevztue

http://tinyurl.com/y9gt468

http://tinyurl.com/ydjx3x5

