On Fri, Feb 5, 2010 at 9:18 AM, Old Volks Home <oldvolkshome(-at-)gmail.com>wrote:

> 1974 is a transitional year on steering column, steering wheel and steering
> lock parts.
>
> Up thru VIN 2x4 2164 059 they only had a bearing in the steering column
> tube, 211-415-585 A and VW obsoleted this way back in December 1988.
>
> From VIN 2x4 2164 060 thru 1979 model year, there are two bearings, the one
> noted above and one above it in the steering lock assembly, 211-415-585 B.
> VW obsoleted this bearing just a few years go.  A quick check with a
> contact
> in Germany has turned up zip, nada, nothing on both part numbers.
